{"type":null,"faqId":19412,"title":"手机发热量大","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{font-family:Frutiger Next Com;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>手机发热主要取决于您使用手机的方式。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>充电时手机发热：充电时发热是普遍现象。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>针对这点华为手机在设计时增加了过热保护电路功能，确保不会因为发热导致电池发生故障或寿命缩短。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>请尽量在阴凉干燥的地方充电。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>另外，建议您不要在充电时进行上网、玩游戏或看视频等高功耗的操作。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>玩游戏时手机发热：玩游戏时，手机 </span><span class=\"s2\">CPU</span><span> 处于高负载状态，会产生较大热量。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>但华为手机均通过国家安规测试，正常使用时的发热不会产生安全风险。建议玩游戏时彻底关闭后台暂时不使用的应用程序，同时请不要在充电时玩游戏。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>使用数据网络时手机发热：使用数据网络时手机的发热程度主要与网络信号强度有关，信号较差时手机发热较大。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>建议您移动到信号强度大的地方后再连接网络。另外，尽量不要开启大量第三方应用程序同时获取网络资源，这样不仅会造成流量突增，同时会增加手机的发热量。在网络信号较弱的地方，尽量不要长时间充电时上网。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>通话时手机发热：请尽量在信号强度较大的地方通话，同时建议您使用耳机进行通话。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>华为会定期在官网发布最新软件版本，以优化软件性能，请您及时升级软件，以体验更好的手机性能。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2553","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1422608228000,"seriesProductName":"G628-TL00","visitedTimes":150,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}